Package net.minecraftforge.common.util

Class Constants.WorldEvents

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.common.util.Constants.WorldEvents
Enclosing class:
Constants
@Deprecated(since="1.17", forRemoval=true) public static class Constants.WorldEvents extends Object
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
Replaced by the constants in LevelEvent. TODO Remove in 1.18
The world event IDS, used when calling Level.globalLevelEvent(int, BlockPos, int).
Can be found from LevelRenderer.globalLevelEvent(int, BlockPos, int)
Some of the events use the data parameter. If this is the case, an explanation of what data does is also provided
